"HAIL MARY FULL OF GRACE.

Image Size: 1660x2360px

Description: 7 Days after the full moon in April, Hail Mary casted 7 Guardian Angels down to earth in search of "The Man With A Vision". It is said in the prophecy that this man is the chosen one skilled with unimaginable artistic abilities and his duty is to show the world his creative talent to inspire and empower people through his creative mind and to wake those who are "slept" on art within the digital world. Will Mother Mary finally find "The Man With a Vision"? 

I am the Man with a Vision.
